{"tid":520803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆料書作者沃爾夫：川普幕僚都說他是弱智、傻子","createTime":"2018-01-05T19:56:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-06T12:41:29.000Z","uid":147314,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"5671a9f169510c6f31b24c547b99f6a93b014542","tid":520803,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T19:56:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180105/1273054/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180105%2F1273054%2F&d=pps9G2sdBXBjOloyVm2RDzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=c3c6b24f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180105%2F1273054%2F&h=6b1b4662\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180105/1273054/</a><br />\n<br />\n爆料書作者沃爾夫：川普身邊人都說他蠢<br />\n<br />\n美國作家沃爾夫（Michael Wolff）在新書《烈焰與怒火》大揭美國總統川普祕辛，成為美國熱門話題，川普批沃爾夫滿紙謊言，沃爾夫周五隔空回應：「我的信用竟被全地球最不可信的人質疑。」<br />\n<br />\n沃爾夫上國家廣播公司《今天》節目受訪，表示他為寫作這本書，所做的訪問都有筆記和錄音佐證，他跟川普本人談過大約3小時，包括大選期間和他就職後，但川普卻說他多次拒絕接受沃爾夫訪問，沃爾夫說：「我絕對跟他談過，他是否明白我在做訪問，我不知道，但絕對不是那種私下閒聊。」他也訪問過許多天天跟川普互動的幕僚。<br />\n<br />\n沃爾夫書中辛辣的內幕，有不少是已去職的白宮策士班農（Steve Bannon）爆料，讓外界質疑這是班農對川普挾怨爆料，沃爾夫說：「這本書主角不是班農，是川普啦。」"},{"pid":"3479dcb4180eedd3e97d2a975b301069a7791a54","tid":520803,"uid":147314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T19:56:26.000Z","msg":"沃爾夫在書中指出，川普多名幕僚都質疑他的智慧、質疑他是否稱職，「他（川普）身邊百分之百的人都這樣想，很多人說他弱智、傻子。」而且大家都說他像個孩子。意即川普有需求就馬上要滿足，凡事都要以他個人為中心。「他不閱讀，他不傾聽，他像個彈珠，只會一直彈來彈去。」<br />\n<br />\n川普請律師發警告函，想要阻止書商出版此書，沃爾夫說：「只會讓書賣得更好，證明書中論點。」他還說：「我該把（感謝）的巧克力送到哪去。」（蔡筱雯／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"9f060cb55111cc20d0faca6ed518bdec2a920e53","tid":520803,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T19:59:28.000Z","msg":"個作家中文又幾好wor"},{"pid":"3eb39bd15323521a25bf0409fe72f0b98c006369","tid":520803,"uid":123264,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T20:02:08.000Z","msg":"弱智都嬴到你<br />\n咁民主黨班精英咪蠢過弱智?"},{"pid":"47fc196d92fbdb8f11440f9325884154daab55c0","tid":520803,"uid":156363,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T20:03:21.000Z","msg":"天氣一凍侵仔就衝出黎話全球暖化呃人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4a9efa32b7377cfd0d5f1ebc058c921fd6dc96f","tid":520803,"uid":90601,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3eb39bd15323521a25bf0409fe72f0b98c006369","tid":520803,"uid":123264,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T20:02:08.000Z","msg":"弱智都嬴到你<br />\n咁民主黨班精英咪蠢過弱智?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T20:05:30.000Z","msg":"因為選民......."},{"pid":"c0d61fe78da2f535585a848b625ee40e29299c5e","tid":520803,"uid":123264,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"b4a9efa32b7377cfd0d5f1ebc058c921fd6dc96f","tid":520803,"uid":90601,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3eb39bd15323521a25bf0409fe72f0b98c006369","tid":520803,"uid":123264,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T20:02:08.000Z","msg":"弱智都嬴到你<br />\n咁民主黨班精英咪蠢過弱智?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T20:05:30.000Z","msg":"因為選民......."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T20:08:11.000Z","msg":"又賴選民蠢<br />\n成日話奧巴馬點好點好 選民咁撚蠢又選到奧巴馬出黎?<br />\n投你就係醒 唔投你就係慒撚<br />\n永遠唔諗下自己有咩問題"},{"pid":"e7394a69e4971f13ff51fb17efe93231365b45bc","tid":520803,"uid":15954,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T20:16:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/f/f4/President_Garrison.png/150px-President_Garrison.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fthumb%2Ff%2Ff4%2FPresident_Garrison.png%2F150px-President_Garrison.png&h=3aabdbe0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"65b249e3ffc066da7aa521b4dac166ce25789dcd","tid":520803,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T20:23:14.000Z","msg":"唔洗佢講都知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3459146f